[{"Id": 1019972, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Reza (a) said: For creating love between husband and wife, if someone recites this name 1001 times on raisin or any other food which is eaten by both husband and wife, having sincere intention, paying full attention towards Almighty Allah and its meaning then love and affection will be established between them...", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Reza (a) farmate hai: Miya biwi mein mohabbat paiyda karne ke liye, agar koi Kishmish (Raisin) ya kisi aur cheez par, jo dono (miya biwi) khaate ho, khuloos’e dil aur uske maaine (meaning) aur Allah (swt) ki taraf tawajjoh karte huwe is zikr ko 1001 martaba padhe to un mein pyaar o mohabbat paiyda hogi…", "UrduDescription": "امام رضاؑ فرماتے ہیں: میاں بیوی میں محبت پیدا کرنے کی غرض سے، اگر کوئی کشمش یا کسی اور چیز پر، جو دونوں (میاں بیوی) کھاتے ہوں، خلوصِ دل اور اس کے معنی اور اللہ تعالی کی طرف توجہ کرتے ہوئے اس ذکر کو ۱۰۰۱ مرتبہ پڑھے تو اُن میں پیار و محبت پیدا ہو گی۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreen